verses.text: \w On|strong="H3068"\w* \w the|strong="H3068"\w* first day \w of|strong="H3068"\w* \w the|strong="H3068"\w* week, \w a|strong="H3068"\w* \w psalm|strong="H4210"\w* \w for|strong="H3068"\w* \w David|strong="H1732"\w*. \w The|strong="H3068"\w* earth \w is|strong="H3068"\w* \w the|strong="H3068"\w* \w Lordâ€™s|strong="H3068"\w* \w and|strong="H3068"\w* \w the|strong="H3068"\w* fulness thereof: \w the|strong="H3068"\w* world, \w and|strong="H3068"\w* all \w they|strong="H3808"\w* \w that|strong="H3068"\w* dwell therein.

\w For|strong="H5921"\w* \w he|strong="H5921"\w* hath founded \w it|strong="H5921"\w* \w upon|strong="H5921"\w* \w the|strong="H5921"\w* seas; \w and|strong="H4325"\w* hath prepared \w it|strong="H5921"\w* \w upon|strong="H5921"\w* \w the|strong="H5921"\w* rivers.

\w Who|strong="H5315"\w* \w shall|strong="H5315"\w* ascend \w into|strong="H7725"\w* \w the|strong="H7725"\w* mountain \w of|strong="H8034"\w* \w the|strong="H7725"\w* Lord: or \w who|strong="H5315"\w* \w shall|strong="H5315"\w* stand \w in|strong="H5315"\w* \w his|strong="H7725"\w* holy place?

\w The|strong="H3588"\w* innocent \w in|strong="H1571"\w* hands, \w and|strong="H7626"\w* clean \w of|strong="H7626"\w* heart, \w who|strong="H3588"\w* hath \w not|strong="H3808"\w* taken \w his|strong="H3588"\w* soul \w in|strong="H1571"\w* vain, \w nor|strong="H3808"\w* sworn deceitfully \w to|strong="H3808"\w* \w his|strong="H3588"\w* neighbour.

\w He|strong="H6440"\w* \w shall|strong="H6440"\w* receive \w a|strong="H6440"\w* blessing \w from|strong="H6440"\w* \w the|strong="H6440"\w* Lord, \w and|strong="H7218"\w* mercy \w from|strong="H6440"\w* God \w his|strong="H6440"\w* Saviour.

\w This|strong="H3068"\w* \w is|strong="H3068"\w* \w the|strong="H3605"\w* generation \w of|strong="H1004"\w* \w them|strong="H7291"\w* \w that|strong="H3605"\w* seek \w him|strong="H3605"\w*, \w of|strong="H1004"\w* \w them|strong="H7291"\w* \w that|strong="H3605"\w* seek \w the|strong="H3605"\w* face \w of|strong="H1004"\w* \w the|strong="H3605"\w* \w God|strong="H3068"\w* \w of|strong="H1004"\w* Jacob.
Lift up your gates, O ye princes, and be ye lifted up, O eternal gates: and the King of Glory shall enter in.
Who is this King of Glory? the Lord who is strong and mighty: the Lord mighty in battle.
Lift up your gates, O ye princes, and be ye lifted up, O eternal gates: and the King of Glory shall enter in.
Who is this King of Glory? the Lord of hosts, he is the King of Glory.
